'''催產素'''（{{lang-en|Oxytocin}}，又称'''缩宫素'''，简称为'''OT'''）是一種[[哺乳類動物|哺乳類動物]][[激素|激素]]，是[[肽类激素|肽类激素]]也是[[神經肽|神經肽]]，一般由[[下視丘|下視丘]]產生，由{{le|腦下垂體#腦下垂體後葉|Posterior pituitary|腦垂腺後葉}}釋放<ref>{{cite book | title = Gray's Anatomy: The Anatomical Basis of Clinical Practice | date = 2015 | publisher = Elsevier Health Sciences | isbn = 978-0-7020-6851-5 | page = 358 | edition = 41 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=b7FVCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA358 }}</ref>。催产素可以在大腦[[下視丘|下視丘]]「室旁核」與「{{link-en|視上核|supraoptic nucleus}}」[[神經元|神經元]]所自然分泌，經下視丘腦下垂體路徑神經纖維送到{{le|垂體後葉|posterior pituitary gland}}分泌。催产素在社會連結、[[有性生殖|有性生殖]]、在[[分娩|分娩]]中及分娩後都相當重要<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Yang|first1=HP|last2=Wang|first2=L|last3=Han|first3=L|last4=Wang|first4=SC|title=Nonsocial functions of hypothalamic oxytocin.|journal=ISRN neuroscience|date=2013|volume=2013|pages=179272|pmid=24967304}}</ref>。催產素在雌性[[哺乳類動物|哺乳類動物]]生產時大量釋放，{{le|子宮頸擴張|Cervical dilation|擴張子宮頸}}和[[子宮收縮|收縮子宮]]，促進[[分娩|分娩]]，分娩後催产素也會刺激[[乳頭|乳頭]]，促進[[乳汁|乳汁]]產生<ref name=Chi2012>{{cite book|last1=Chiras|first1=Daniel D.|title=Human biology|date=2012|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|location=Sudbury, MA|isbn=9780763783457|page=262|edition=7th ed.|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=mqlY1n8Ez1oC&pg=PA262|access-date=2016-01-25|archive-date=2019-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190511101205/https://books.google.ca/books?id=mqlY1n8Ez1oC&pg=PA262|dead-url=no}}</ref>，有助於生產、{{le|母嬰連結|maternal bonding}}及[[哺乳|哺乳]]<ref name=Chi2012/><ref>{{cite book|title=Human Evolutionary Biology|date=2010|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=9781139789004|page=282|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=3NRf_8gwmO8C&pg=PA282|access-date=2016-01-25|archive-date=2020-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018070623/https://books.google.ca/books?id=3NRf_8gwmO8C&pg=PA282|dead-url=no}}</ref>。催产素是於1906年由[[亨利·哈利特·戴尔|亨利·哈利特·戴尔]]發現<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1113/jphysiol.1906.sp001148 |pmid=16992821 |pmc=1465771 |title=On some physiological actions of ergot |journal=The Journal of Physiology |volume=34 |issue=3 |pages=163–206 |year=1906 |last1=Dale |first1=H. H }}</ref>，在1952年確定其分子結構<ref>{{cite book | last1 = Corey | first1 = E.J. | name-list-format = vanc | title = Molecules and Medicine | date = 2012 | publisher = John Wiley & Sons | isbn = 978-1-118-36173-3 | chapter-url = https://books.google.com/books?id=jz2GN6DYoOoC&lpg=RA1-PT108&pg=RA1-PT110 | chapter = Oxytocin | access-date = 2019-03-18 | archive-date = 2019-05-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190511094718/https://books.google.com/books?id=jz2GN6DYoOoC&lpg=RA1-PT108&pg=RA1-PT110 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

[[催產素_(藥物)|作為藥物的催產素]]可以幫助生產<ref name="IUPHAR Oxytocin summary">{{cite web | title=Oxytocin: Summary | url=http://www.guidetopharmacology.org/GRAC/LigandDisplayForward?tab=summary&ligandId=2174 | website=IUPHAR/BPS guide to pharmacology | publisher=International Union of Basic and Clinical Pharmacology | accessdate=14 December 2016 | quote=Endogenous oxytocin is a hormone and neuropeptide, which plays a role in social bonding, sexual reproduction and is required during and after childbirth. Purified oxytocin is used clinically. | archive-date=2020-10-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025075107/https://www.guidetopharmacology.org/GRAC/LigandDisplayForward?tab=summary&ligandId=2174 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=AHFS2015>{{cite web|title=Oxytocin|url=https://www.drugs.com/monograph/oxytocin.html|publisher=The American Society of Health-System Pharmacists|access-date=1 June 2015|archive-date=2015-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150520014256/http://www.drugs.com/monograph/oxytocin.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book | title = The Oxford Handbook of Prosocial Behavior | date = 2015 | publisher = Oxford University Press | isbn = 978-0-19-539981-3 | page = 354 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=EfzOBwAAQBAJ&pg=PA354 }}</ref>，且早在1911年，醫生就已在臨床上應用含有催產素的腦下垂體萃取物，也就所謂的「后叶催产素」，來促進子宮收縮以對治難產的問題。<ref>{{cite web
