==簡介==
催產素英文單詞{{lang|en|Oxytocin}}是來自希臘語「{{lang|el|ὼκυτοκίνη}}，{{lang|el|ōkytokínē}}」，意思是“快誕生”，其子宮收縮性質分別由英國藥理學家[[亨利·哈利特·戴爾|亨利·哈利特·戴爾]]在1906年發現的<ref name="pmid16992821">{{cite journal | author = Dale HH | title = On some physiological actions of ergot | journal = J. Physiol. (Lond.) | volume = 34 | issue = 3 | pages = 163–206 | date = 1906-05 | pmid = 16992821 | pmc = 1465771 | doi =  }}</ref>。催奶性能由奧特（Ott）和斯科特（Scott）於1910年<ref>Ott I, Scott JC. The Action of Infundibulum upon Mammary Secretion. Proc Soc Exp Biol. (1910) p.8:48–49.</ref>和謝弗（Schafer）和Mackenzie於1911年描述<ref>Schafer EA, Mackenzie K. ''The action of animal extracts on milk secretion''. Proceedings of the Royal Society of London Series B-Containing Papers of a Biological Character. (1911) p.84:16–22.</ref>。

1953年初科學家[[文森特·迪维尼奥|文森特·迪维尼奥]]的團隊和Tuppy成功測定排列出催產素的九個氨基酸序列<ref name="pmid13129273">{{cite journal | author = du Vigneaud V, Ressler C, Trippett S | title = The sequence of amino acids in oxytocin, with a proposal for the structure of oxytocin | journal = J. Biol. Chem. | volume = 205 | issue = 2 | pages = 949–57 | date = 1953-12 | pmid = 13129273 | doi =  }}</ref>。後在1953年科學家文森特·迪维尼奥的團隊合成了可應用到為婦女[[催生|催生]]的[[人工合成催產素|人工合成催產素]]。1955年，迪维尼奥因此獲得[[諾貝爾化學奬|諾貝爾化學奬]]<ref>{{Cite journal | author = du Vigneaud V, Ressler C, Swan JM, Roberts CW, Katsoyannis PG, Gordon S | title = The synthesis of an octapeptide amide with the hormonal activity of oxytocin | journal = J. Am. Chem. Soc. | volume = 75 | issue = 19 | pages = 4879–80 | year = 1953 | pmid =  | doi = 10.1021/ja01115a553 | url = http://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ja01115a553 | access-date = 2012-04-10 | archive-date = 2019-09-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190913044659/https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ja01115a553 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=Ressler_1954>{{cite journal | author = du Vigneaud V, Ressler C, Swan JM, Roberts CW, Katsoyannis PG | title = The synthesis of oxytocin | journal = J. Am. Chem. Soc. | date = 1954-06 | volume = 76 | issue = 12 | pages = 3115–3121 | doi = 10.1021/ja01641a004}}</ref>。催產素是第一個被測序和合成的[[神经肽|神经肽]]。文森特·迪维尼奥1954年出版指出這個合成是第一個神经肽的合成<ref>THE SYNTHESIS OF OXYTOCIN.  Vincent du Vigneaud, Charlotte Ressler, John M. Swan, Carleton W. Roberts, Panayotis G. Katsoyannis  1954  J. Am. Chem. Soc., 1954, 76（12）,pp 3115–3121</ref>。

==結構==
[[File:Oxytocin-neurophysin.png|thumb]]
催产素是由九个[[氨基酸|氨基酸]]组成的[[多肽|多肽]]构成的，[[人類|人類]]與大多數[[哺乳動物|哺乳動物]]的催產素的化學結構如下：
<div style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: red">[[半胱氨酸|半胱氨酸]]─[[酪氨酸|酪氨酸]]─[[異亮氨酸|異亮氨酸]]─[[穀氨醯胺|穀氨醯胺]]-[[天冬醯胺|天冬醯胺]]-[[半胱氨酸|半胱氨酸]]-[[脯氨酸|脯氨酸]]-[[亮氨酸|亮氨酸]]-[[甘氨酸|甘氨酸]]─ [[氨基|NH<sub>2</sub>]]</span></div>

催產素的結構和[[抗利尿激素|抗利尿激素]]（[[半胱氨酸|半胱氨酸]]─[[酪氨酸|酪氨酸]]─[[苯丙氨酸|苯丙氨酸]]─[[穀氨醯胺|穀氨醯胺]]-[[天冬氨酸|天冬氨酸]]-[[半胱氨酸|半胱氨酸]]-[[脯氨酸|脯氨酸]]-[[精氨酸|精氨酸]]-[[甘氨酸|甘氨酸]]─ NH<sub>2</sub>）非常相似。催產素和抗利尿激素由[[文森特·迪维尼奥|文森特·迪维尼奥]]於1953年分離出和[[化学合成|合成]]，使他獲得1955年諾貝爾化學獎，從人類[[腦下垂體|腦下垂體]]釋放的激素中，目前只有發現这两種激素是會在一段距離作用。

==功能==
最近的研究已經開始探討催產素對於各種行為的影響，包括[[性高潮|性高潮]]、社會認同、夫妻或情侶間的{{link-en|成對結合|pair bonding}}、[[焦慮|焦慮]]，和產婦的行為等<ref name="pmid19482229">{{Cite journal|author=Lee HJ, Macbeth AH, Pagani JH, Young WS |title=Oxytocin: the Great Facilitator of Life |journal=Progress in Neurobiology |volume=88 |issue=2 |pages=127–51 |date=2009-06 |pmid=19482229 |doi=10.1016/j.pneurobio.2009.04.001 |pmc=2689929}}</ref>。出於這個原因，它有時被稱為“愛情激素”。催產素有助於減輕壓力及緩解疼痛<ref name="康健">{{cite journal |author=梁煙純 |date=2005-10 |title=用雙手安撫肌肉的情緒 |journal=康健雜誌 |volume=83期 |url=http://www.commonhealth.com.tw/article/article.action?id=5016721 |accessdate=2012-04-12 |quote= |archive-date=2019-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190512094943/http://www.commonhealth.com.tw/article/article.action?id=5016721 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。無法分泌催產素，與無法感到同情，[[反社會|反社會]]，[[精神病|精神病]]，[[自戀|自戀]]及一般的[[控制狂|操控個性]]有關<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1992405,00.html |title=Thanks, Mom! |author=O'Callaghan, Tiffany |date=7 June 2010 |work=Time Magazine |publisher=Time, Inc. |accessdate=2010-06-08 |archive-date=2010-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100531195557/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1992405,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

