===自閉症===
[[自閉症|自閉症]]患者血液中的催產素濃度很低<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mag.udn.com/mag/life/storypage.jsp?f_ART_ID=452070 |title=腦中催產素不足 人會欠缺同理心 - 精神健康 - 疾病大全 - udn健康醫藥 |accessdate=2014-01-18 |archive-date=2014-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140121031133/http://mag.udn.com/mag/life/storypage.jsp?f_ART_ID=452070 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。小兒神經科醫生指出 ，[[馬術|騎馬]]會促使身體釋放催產素 ，如此一來能夠開啟學習的接收器，適用於自閉症以及[[亞斯伯格症候群|亞斯伯格症候群]]<ref>{{cite news
|title=騎馬可治童自閉 阿根廷籲納健保
|url=http://news.pts.org.tw/detail.php?NEENO=182540
|author=王蕙文
|publisher=公視新聞網
|accessdate=2012-05-27
|archive-date=2015-07-11
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150711090338/http://news.pts.org.tw/detail.php?NEENO=182540
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。催產素可能是一個有效的治療[[自閉症|自閉症]]的重複行為的處方藥<ref>{{Cite journal|author=Bartz JA, Hollander E |title=Oxytocin and experimental therapeutics in autism spectrum disorders |journal=Progress in Brain Research |volume=170 |issue= |pages=451–62 |year=2008 |pmid=18655901 |doi=10.1016/S0079-6123（08）00435-4|series=Progress in Brain Research|isbn=978-0-444-53201-5}}</ref>，儘管美國國家自閉症協會（National Autism Association）認為要利用催產素來治療自閉仍言之過早<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://mag.udn.com/mag/life/storypage.jsp?f_ART_ID=489029 |title=美國研究：催產素 改善自閉童社交行為 - 關懷自閉症 - 疾病大全 - udn健康醫藥 |accessdate=2014-01-18 |archive-date=2014-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140121031128/http://mag.udn.com/mag/life/storypage.jsp?f_ART_ID=489029 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==藥物形式==
催產素鼻腔噴霧劑已用於刺激母乳喂養，但這種方法的有效性是值得懷疑的<ref name="pmid16223754">{{Cite journal|author=Fewtrell MS, Loh KL, Blake A, Ridout DA, Hawdon J |title=Randomised, double blind trial of oxytocin nasal spray in mothers expressing breast milk for preterm infants |journal=Archives of Disease in Childhood. Fetal and Neonatal Edition |volume=91 |issue=3 |pages=F169–74 |date=2006-05 |pmid=16223754 |pmc=2672698 |doi=10.1136/adc.2005.081265}}</ref>。

